Imbuto
Imbuto, imbuto, imbuto.

Imbuto ziraryoha.

Abantu barya ubwoko butandukanye bwimbuto.

Umwe ashobora kurya imyembe, undi ashobora kurya inanasi.

Twishimira amacunga.

Abana bishimira pome.

Inyoni zishimira ibigori. 
Oooh imbuto ni nziza kubuzima. Abantu, inyamaswa ninyoni bakunda imbuto cyane.
